title: Nikolai Vovk
text:
Nikolai Aleksandrovich Vovk (; born 8 January 1997) is a Russian <a href="association%20football">football</a> player.
Club career.
He made his debut in the <a href="Russian%20Football%20National%20League">Russian Football National League</a> for <a href="FC%20Shinnik%20Yaroslavl">FC Shinnik Yaroslavl</a> on 22 March 2015 in a game against <a href="FC%20Luch-Energiya%20Vladivostok">FC Luch-Energiya Vladivostok</a>.
